schools.name: Joyce Clark Middle School (Formerly Sierra Vista M

data.description: This upgraded 4BR/2BA, 2014 sq.ft. home is centrally located in Sierra Vista, AZ minutes from Ft. Huachuca, shopping, schools & Canyon Vista Medical Center. This lovely home has central air conditioning (central A/C) with a UV air cleaner/sanitizer built into the ductwork. Large open living spaces with a new gas fireplace. Very large primary bedroom with two walk-in double closets. Plenty of kitchen cabinets. Newer kitchen appliances, large laundry room and amazing screened porch to enjoy the outdoors. Tasteful LVP flooring and tile throughout. An RV gate gives you plenty of access to the back yard. Come by and take a look before it's gone! Call today.
